                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/9749" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">OM-0377</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">884 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">黑土地遇见“数字”基因，解锁北大荒“智慧”农业密码</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">When Black Soil Meets Digital DNA: Deciphering the Code of Intelligent Agriculture in China&#39;s Beidahuang</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">韩楠，任素晓，吕伟聪，崔怡迪，李航</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">燕山大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">北大荒农垦集团有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">农林牧副渔业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">生产运营部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">15 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">北大荒；数字化转型；现代农业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"> Beidahuang; digital transformation; modern agriculture</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">在全球农业加速迈入4.0时代的浪潮中，黑龙江北大荒农垦集团作为中国农业现代化主力军，积极响应国家号召，以国家粮食安全战略为引领，率先开启数字化转型征程，以科技创新为驱动，力求突破传统农业生产的局限，探索出一条高效、可持续的现代农业发展之路。本案例完整呈现北大荒利用数字技术从机械化垦殖到数字农服生态的转型历程以及成果。通过深入剖析北大荒数字化转型实践，帮助学生理解数字化转型相关知识，掌握企业数字化转型的核心要点，包括技术应用和业务流程重构等内容。同时，鼓励学生思考如何用北大荒数字化转型的实践助力中国农业现代化进程和乡村振兴战略的实施。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">In the wave of global agriculture accelerating into the 4.0 era, Heilongjiang Beidahuang Agricultural Reclamation Group, as the main force of China&#39;s agricultural modernization, actively responds to the national call, takes the national food security strategy as the guide, takes the lead in embarking on the journey of digital transformation, and is driven by technological innovation, striving to break through the limitations of traditional agricultural production and explore an efficient and sustainable path for modern agricultural development. This case fully presents the transformation process and achievements of Beidahuang&#39;s use of digital technology from mechanized cultivation to digital agricultural service ecology. By deeply analyzing the digital transformation practices of Beidahuang, we aim to help students understand the relevant knowledge of digital transformation and master the core points of enterprise digital transformation, including technology application and business process reconstruction. At the same time, encourage students to think about how to use the practice of Beidahuang&#39;s digital transformation to assist in the modernization of Chinese agriculture and the implementation of rural revitalization strategies.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">改编/二手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2022</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《运营管理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">数字化转型理论；数字化转型驱动因素；数字化转型阶段理论；新质生产力</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2025-08</td>
